Resolução¶

$(f \cdot g) \ (x,y) = f (g \ (x,y)) = f (x+y) = succ (2*(x+y)) = 2*x + 2*y + 1$

$(f \cdot g) \ (x,y)$

{ lei (72) }

$= \ f \ (g \ (x,y))$

{ def. $g$ }

$= \ f \ (x + y)$

{ def. $f$ }

$= (succ \cdot (2*)) (x + y)$

{ lei (72) }

$= succ \ ((2*)\ (x+y))$

{ prop. distributiva da multiplicao em relao adio }

$= succ \ (2x + 2y)$

{def. $succ$}

$=2x + 2y + 1$

In [7]:
f = succ . (2*)
g (x,y) = x+y

-- type checking

:t f
:t g
:t (f . g)
f :: forall c. (Enum c, Num c) => c -> c
g :: forall a. Num a => (a, a) -> a
(f . g) :: forall c. (Enum c, Num c) => (c, c) -> c
In [8]:
